{"tid":2490184,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"進擊的巨人2大未解之謎","createTime":"2021-04-15T11:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T11:51:02.000Z","uid":393927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1a819ef42e6a8aabd6a0ec0087fd2eb246d55eea","tid":2490184,"uid":393927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:47:44.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong>含劇透, 小心!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>我個人認為進擊的巨人2大未解之謎</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>1.艾倫做乜變咗隻雀? </strong><br />\n<br />\n完全無解釋到, <br />\n我個人諗法喺創哥想個結局唔好咁sad, 算喺畀少少安慰米卡莎<br />\n<br />\n同埋艾倫變咗做隻雀喺代表艾倫終於自由喇, <br />\n一嚟唔使再做人, 可以做隻雀, 無拘無束, 自由自在咁飛翔, <br />\n二嚟亦代表咗唔使再煩人世間嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HuHfQDd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHuHfQDd.jpg&h=8f821ec1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2.阿克曼一族誕生之謎?</strong><br />\n<br />\n都仲未知阿克曼一族喺點誕生嘅, 淨喺知阿克曼一族自古已經喺效力王, 但無解釋過喺點誕生<br />\n<br />\n淨喺知吉克講過阿克曼喺巨人科學嘅產物, 但實際喺點製造出嚟喺無解釋過嘅, <br />\n巨人科學即喺點做阿克曼一族出嚟?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2021/04/15/194602_e027c9b2bba8b6306e41e06e5be0a5e8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2021%2F04%2F15%2F194602_e027c9b2bba8b6306e41e06e5be0a5e8.png&h=c140860e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>歡迎各位留言討論</strong>"},{"pid":"a442ed7bd663b2fd712e08430574496ff68bf536","tid":2490184,"uid":393927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:49:06.000Z","msg":"聞說單行本會增加結局嘅頁數, 希望創哥會寫好啲個結局 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467e08d1075c4d535dff6534458ce4e17101b98b","tid":2490184,"uid":38953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:50:16.000Z","msg":"我覺得1唔洗深究<br />\n你當佢轉世又好，隻鳥根本唔係艾倫都得，係mikasa角度覺得係艾倫姐"},{"pid":"fb4369783b388bbc7e6a72b3e44907198ae5a24f","tid":2490184,"uid"